  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective study to extensively evaluate subjective patient parameters on quality
      of life, reflux-symptoms, side effects, medication-use and measurements of esophageal
      manometry and Impedance-pH-Monitoring after Full-Thickness-Gastroplication.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
